# =========================
# Backtest / market data
# =========================
# "data/" (not "data/") so the negation below can still re-include the checked-in sample
# fixture -- a directory-matching pattern would prune the whole folder from traversal and
# no !exception could reach inside it.
data/*
datasets/
historical_data/
backtest_data/
*.parquet
*.feather
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.sqlite
*.db

# ถ้าต้องการเก็บ sample data ขนาดเล็ก ให้ใช้ folder นี้แทน
!data_sample/
!data_sample/**

# Sample OHLCV fixture used by the replay backtest CLI/tests -- small, synthetic, meant
# to be checked in (unlike real historical market data dumps, which stay ignored above).
!data/sample_m1.csv

# =========================
